  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <!-- 12. FINAL CTA                                                     -->
  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <CTASection variant="invert" size="lg" id="final-cta">
    <h2 slot="heading">The money's in your inbox.</h2>
    <p slot="description">
      Tomorrow morning you could wake up, open your daily brief, and know exactly who to message. Start with the free playbook.
    </p>
